OL,5, The US company behind Tasers plans to  
OL,6, produce stun gun-armed drones it claims
OL,7, will help stop school shootings.       
OL,9,FThe Arizona-based company, Axon, says  
OL,10,Fthat the high-tech solution is         
OL,11,Fnecessary amid a "fruitless" debate on 
OL,12,Fgun policy in the US.                  
OL,14,FThe announcement, however, earned a    
OL,15,Fstern rebuke from the company's own    
OL,16,Fethics board.                          
OL,18,FNearly 30 school shootings have taken  
OL,19,Fplace in the US this year.             
